ORG_GOAL: "reducing poverty and helping the poor meet their basic needs"
ORG_GOAL_S: "kupunguza umasikini na kusaidia watu maskini kuafikia mahitaji yao ya kimsingi"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."       //       "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."    //     "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

ORG_MESSAGE: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals." / "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."

ORG_GOAL: "reducing poverty and helping the poor meet their basic needs"
ORG_GOAL_S: "kupunguza umasikini na kusaidia watu maskini kuafikia mahitaji yao ya kimsingi"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."       //       "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."    //     "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals." / "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."

ORG_GOAL: "enabling people to support those they care about and help the community grow together"
ORG_GOAL_S: "kuwezesha watu kuunga mkono wale wanaowajali na kusaidia jamii kuendelea pamoja"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals." / "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."

The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them." / "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

ORG_GOAL_S: "kuwezesha watu kuunga mkono wale wanaowajali na kusaidia jamii kuendelea pamoja"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals." / "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."

ORG_GOAL: "enabling people to support those they care about and help the community grow together"
ORG_GOAL_S: "kuwezesha watu kuunga mkono wale wanaowajali na kusaidia jamii kuendelea pamoja"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals." / "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."

ORG_GOAL_S: "kupunguza umasikini na kusaidia watu maskini kuafikia mahitaji yao ya kimsingi"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."       //       "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."    //     "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

ORG_GOAL: "reducing poverty and helping the poor meet their basic needs"
ORG_GOAL_S: "kupunguza umasikini na kusaidia watu maskini kuafikia mahitaji yao ya kimsingi"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."       //       "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."    //     "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

ORG_GOAL: "enabling individuals to pursue personal goals and become more financially independent"
ORG_GOAL_S: "kuwezesha watu binafsi kufuata malengo yao ya kibinafsi na wakue wakijitegemea kifedha zaidi"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them." / "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them." / "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them." / "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them." / "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."

ORG_GOAL: "enabling people to support those they care about and help the community grow together"
ORG_GOAL_S: "kuwezesha watu kuunga mkono wale wanaowajali na kusaidia jamii kuendelea pamoja"
ORG_MESSAGE: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The "Individual Empowerment Organization" aims to promote individuals' potential to create a better future for themselves. The organization believes that individuals are wise and know best how to help themselves become self-reliant/independent if they have the financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals." / "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."

Thus, the –Individual Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to individuals, like you, to enable them to invest in their personal goals."
ORG_MESSAGE_S: "Hili "Shirika la Kuimarisha mtu Binafsi" lina lenga kukuza uwezo wa watu binafsi ili kujenga maisha bora ya usoni kwao wenyewe. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu ni wenye hekima na wanajua vizuri kujisaidia wenyewe ili kujitegemea kama tu wako na rasilimali ya kuwawezesha kufanya hivo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA WATU BINAFSI" linapeana rasilimali ya kifedha kwa watu binafsi kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuwekeza katika malengo yao binafsi."
ORG_MESSAGE_2: "The "Poverty Alleviation Organization" aims to reduce poverty and ease the burden of financial hardship among the poor. This organization believes that people living in poverty should be given income support to help them meet their basic needs. Thus, the "Poverty Alleviation Organization" gives financial charity to poor people to help them sustain themselves and experience less hardship." / "Hili "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" lina lengo la kupunguza umaskini na kurahisisha hali ngumu ya kifedha kati ya watu maskini.  Hili shirika linaamini kuwa watu maskini wanafaa kusaidiwa kipato ili kuikimu mahitaji yao ya msingi. / Kwa hiyo, "Shirika la Kupunguza Umaskini" linatoa msaada wa kifedha kwa watu kama wewe, kuwasaidia kupata mahitaji ya kimsingi na kukidhi hali na kakabiliana na dharura."
ORG_MESSAGE_3: "The –Community Empowerment Organization” aims to enable people to help promote better futures for those they care about and want to support most. The organization believes that people know best how to support each other and grow together if they have financial resources to do so. Thus, the –Community Empowerment Organization” gives financial resources to community members, like you, to enable them to contribute positively to the lives of people important to them." / "Hili "Shirika la kuimarisha Jamii" lina lengo la kuwezesha watu kukuza maisha bora ya usoni ya wale wanaowajali na wanaotaka kusaidia zaidi. Shirika hili linaamini kuwa watu wanafahamu vyema vile wanaweza saidia watu wengine na kuimarika pamoja kama wako na rasilimali ya kufanya hivyo. Kwa hivyo,"SHIRIKA LA KUIMARISHA JAMII" linapeana rasilimali za kifedha kwa watu wa jamii kama wewe ili kuwawezesha kuchangia vyema kwa maisha ya watu muhimu kwao."
